overview: AIR - Concert Prive  Studio 104, La Plaine Saint Denis, France  May 05, 2007  Setlist:  Napalm Love  Talisman  People In The City  Mer Du Japon  Beauty Mark *  Everything I Cannot See *  Don't Be Light  Kelly Watch The Stars  Somewhere Between Walking and Sleeping **  La Femme d'Argent  + Interview  A great and nice concert by this band with some guests such  as Charlotte Gainsbourg (*) and Neil Hannon (**) (from the divine comedy).
title: Air - Concert Prive
